## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **React** - UI framework
- **Vite** - Build tool
- **TypeScript** - Type-safe JavaScript
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework

### Backend
- **Node.js** - Runtime environment
- **Express.js** - Web application framework

### AI & Automation
- **Ollama** - Fine-tuned Local LLM with legal data
- **n8n** - AI workflow automation

### Infrastructure & DevOps
- **Ubuntu Server LTS** - Server operating system
- **NGINX** - Reverse proxy & web server
- **SSH** - Secure remote administration
- **Docker** - Containerization & service isolation
- **Self-Hosted Private Cloud** - Data privacy and control

### Security
- **Twingate** - Zero-trust remote access
- **ZTNA Architecture** - Zero-trust network access
- **Identity-Based Access Control** - Secure authentication
- **Encrypted Tunnel Communication** - Secure data transmission
- **Role-Based Access Control** - Lawyers, admins, and end users

